{"tid":683614,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【遲來的婚戒】未婚夫癌逝 她3個月後收到對方的驚喜","createTime":"2018-05-30T00:22:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-30T01:25:59.000Z","uid":48083,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cfab10bf0b86c1b31dc918e2a20649a54555572c","tid":683614,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T00:22:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/30/082122_866aebafad3dab1b1219045c9561a73a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F30%2F082122_866aebafad3dab1b1219045c9561a73a.png&h=88f760ec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/30/082139_3d2de89f2e86fd4304b932ca527c218b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F30%2F082139_3d2de89f2e86fd4304b932ca527c218b.png&h=bdf73cc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n英國肯特郡一名女子本來想盡快與患血癌的未婚夫結婚，未料對方在婚前死亡，更令準新娘意想不到是，在未婚夫死後3個月收到他親自設計的訂婚戒指，「我會永遠珍惜它」。<br />\n<br />\n坎伯禾夫（Danielle Cumberworth）本來打算與27歲未婚夫史密斯（Ashley Grant-Smith）於去年10月結婚，但史密斯卻10月9日死亡。今年1月、即史密斯死後3個月，坎伯禾夫收到未婚夫生前訂製的訂婚戒指。<br />\n<br />\n坎伯禾夫憶述她下班回家發現送貨員曾到訪的通知，當她親自前往領取包裹時，才知道是訂婚戒指，「（我）真是十分意外，我沒有哭，我笑了。他從未告訴我，這是一隻漂亮的白金鑽石戒指。」<br />\n<br />\n兩人於2015年相識交往，翌年2月史密斯頸部腫塊越來越大，接受血液檢查後證實患上罕見血癌T細胞淋巴瘤（T-cell lymphoma）。他先後接受18次化療及放射治療，去年8月本來獲自願者捐贈幹細胞進行移植手術，可惜病情急轉直下，身體太虛弱無法做手術，癌細胞後來擴散全身。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180529/58246026\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180529%2F58246026&d=YPZKdr1hWSu%2FId2ZQmbT9P755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=4c195578\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180529%2F58246026&h=c7010423\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180529/58246026</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b5d91667f8cec45628de7cf6be0023072fdb62d","tid":683614,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T00:37:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc35e8eb7c83661b8f71cd9649bd0c05d94d7808","tid":683614,"uid":63588,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T01:00:51.000Z","msg":"換做香港女人會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"771f328a775dcb8128fb9bb36feadf50a0b98c6f","tid":683614,"uid":130901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fc35e8eb7c83661b8f71cd9649bd0c05d94d7808","tid":683614,"uid":63588,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T01:00:51.000Z","msg":"換做香港女人會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T01:02:11.000Z","msg":"感動，之後爭遺產"},{"pid":"16ab7c4b96f09ea7a0569d2fd7e4660df129750f","tid":683614,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"771f328a775dcb8128fb9bb36feadf50a0b98c6f","tid":683614,"uid":130901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fc35e8eb7c83661b8f71cd9649bd0c05d94d7808","tid":683614,"uid":63588,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T01:00:51.000Z","msg":"換做香港女人會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T01:02:11.000Z","msg":"感動，之後爭遺產"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T01:25:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}